WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.512
We have been trying for almost a decade to get thousands 

00:00:03.512 --> 00:00:07.086
of illegal immigrants from Islamic countries to storm our 

00:00:07.086 --> 00:00:10.907
borders and threaten the safety of our streets day after day. 

00:00:10.907 --> 00:00:15.672
The measures taken to avoid this are irrelevant. 

00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:19.409
In the Mediterranean, 

00:00:19.409 --> 00:00:23.172
grants are given to NGOs that, 

00:00:23.172 --> 00:00:27.662
far from providing humanitarian aid, 

00:00:27.662 --> 00:00:32.273
actively collaborate in this process, 

00:00:32.273 --> 00:00:36.885
making the work of the mafias easier, 

00:00:36.885 --> 00:00:43.802
mafias that have taken the lives of thousands of people. 

00:00:43.802 --> 00:00:48.900
of Europe on the stage of 1 horror movie. 
